        <Parent_String>playgrounds [300008203], sports and recreation spaces [300122433], open spaces by function [300129929], open spaces [300008072], Open Spaces and Site Elements (hierarchy name ) [300139081], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
